import houseCompare from "./components/houseCompare";
export default {
  data() {
    return {
      show: true
    };
  },
  // components: {
  //   SiderMenu

  mounted() {
    var roleid = JSON.parse(sessionStorage.getItem("roleId"));

      this.show = true;
    } else {
      this.show = false;
    }

      this.$root.Bus.$emit("eventCompare");
    }
  },

    houseCompare
  }
};
